sources.title: A Fistful Of Lead | Full Action Western Movie
sources.description:
A Fistful Of Lead - Four of the West's most infamous outlaws carry out a daring bank heist in the gold-rush town, Bath Water. As the posse takes chase, things take a turn for the worse, as the bandits realize they've been double-crossed - but by who?
2018.  Stars: James Groom, Tom Nolan, Duncan Casey
